[I] A featureful union filesystem

[T] Mergerfs is a union filesystem geared towards simplifying storage and
[T] management of files across numerous commodity storage devices. It is
[T] similar to mhddfs, unionfs, and aufs.

[U] https://github.com/trapexit/mergerfs

